	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَلَئِنۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَرۡسَلۡنَا رِيحٗا <a data-content='فرَأوُا النّبات مُصفرّا بعد الخُضرة' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>فَرَأَوۡهُ مُصۡفَرّٗا</a> لَّظَلُّواْ مِنۢ بَعۡدِهِۦ </div><div>يَكۡفُرُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٥١</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَإِنَّكَ لَا تُسۡمِعُ ٱلۡمَوۡتَىٰ وَلَا تُسۡمِعُ ٱلصُّمَّ ٱلدُّعَآءَ إِذَا </div><div>وَلَّوۡاْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مُدۡبِرِينَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٥٢ وَمَآ أَنتَ بِهَٰدِ ٱلۡعُمۡيِ عَن ضَلَٰلَتِهِمۡۖ إِن تُسۡمِعُ </div><div>إِلَّا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مَن</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> يُؤۡمِنُ بِ‍َٔايَٰتِنَا فَهُم مُّسۡلِمُونَ ٥٣ ۞ٱللَّهُ ٱلَّذِي </div><div>خَلَقَكُم</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>مِّن</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ضَعۡفٖ ثُمَّ جَعَلَ مِنۢ بَعۡدِ ضَعۡفٖ قُوَّةٗ ثُمَّ جَعَلَ مِنۢ </div><div>بَعۡدِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>قُوَّةٖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ضَعۡفٗا <a data-content='حال الشّيخوخة والهرم' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَشَيۡبَةٗۚ</a> يَخۡلُقُ مَا يَشَآءُۚ وَهُوَ ٱلۡعَلِيمُ </div><div>ٱلۡقَدِيرُ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٥٤</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَيَوۡمَ تَقُومُ ٱلسَّاعَةُ يُقۡسِمُ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُونَ مَا لَ