لِكَ يَطۡبَعُ ٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِ ٱلَّذِينَ لَا </div><div>يَعۡلَمُونَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>٥٩</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَٱصۡبِرۡ إِنَّ وَعۡدَ ٱللَّهِ حَقّٞۖ <a data-content='لا يحْمِلنّك على الخفّة والقلق' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>وَلَا يَسۡتَخِفَّنَّكَ</a> ٱلَّذِينَ لَا يُوقِنُونَ </div><div>٦٠</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
